<br>
Here are a few general points, and some tips for speeding up your application process:<br>
<br>
The officers run many raids, and are generally kept quite busy with a myriad of issues, and as a result can't respond in a timely fashion consistently to all applicants.  My advice...if you have friends in the horde, contatct one of them when you see us raiding and ask them to determine if it is possible to join a HoS.  We get to meet you, and see how ya play.  If possible, do a /w all horde, if you see a raid in progress, don't send a tell to an officer, raids take alot of our focus, and likely you will get a resposnse that doesn't seem overly friendly, despite our easy going nature.<br>
<br>
Things we look for:  <br>
<br>
At the expense of sounding elitist, we would rather guild a 58+ with an epic, over a low 50 without one.  We raid alot, so it becomes difficult to get as much time for experience groups, and as such, a preference is given to applicants with a higher level.  Again we go case by case, don't let this scare you, it is just a reality.  Faction is an issue, must be non kos to CoV to get all you can from the horde.  <br>
<br>
We look at other guilds boards, so if you apply to several power guilds and hope to land in one, we know about it, and it detracts from your attractiveness to us.  We aren't a fall back option.<br>
<br>
Understand our loot policy, ask people in our guild their expereinces, and make sure this is an environment that compliments your playing style.  <br>
<br>
Maturity is a must.  Flamers, people who enjoying cussing, or making lewd comments in guild speak, won't find themselves in their element.  A mature person behind the toon fits in instantly, a hothead will find a new guild if they manage to slip in.<br>
<br>
Thanks for your time,<br>
<br>
Baraniel,<br>
Officer of the Horde <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/fhordeofshadows15583frm7.showPrevMessage?topicID=177.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/fhordeofshadows15583frm7.showNextMessage?topicID=177.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/fhordeofshadows15583frm7.emailToFriend?topicID=177.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/fhordeofshadows15583frm7.threadControl?topicID=177.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/grunge/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/fhordeofshadows15583frm7.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=177.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/fhordeofshadows15583frm7.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=177.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub94.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="hordeofshadows15583frm6">HoS General<option value="hordeofshadows15583frm7">HoS Applications<option value="hordeofshadows15583frm2">Hos Private<option value="hordeofshadows15583frm3">HoS Raids<option value="hordeofshadows15583frm5">Epic Status<option value="hordeofshadows15583frm10">HoS Guild Bank<option value="hordeofshadows15583frm11">Trade Skills<option value="hordeofshadows15583frm12">Tactics<option value="hordeofshadows15583frm28">Impor